&lt;p&gt;I'm addicted to my phone and I hate it. I knew it's bad. People wrote papers, &lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/our-crisis-is-not-loneliness-but-human-beings-becoming-invisible"&gt;essays&lt;/a&gt;
and &lt;a href="https://homolova.sk/blog/phone-addiction/"&gt;blog posts&lt;/a&gt; about it. 
Finally, I started feeling it on my own skin.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to papers by &lt;a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC10852174/"&gt;Devi et al.&lt;/a&gt;
and  &lt;a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC10353947/"&gt;Muppalla et al.&lt;/a&gt;, who researched screen-time impact on children and adults correspondingly,
excessive screen media usage has predominantly negative effects.&lt;/p&gt;
